				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 17 Nov 2020 18:19:19 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Petronec</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1967573</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>&quot;The location of SCP-4860 is highly sensitive and indefinitely classified, known only by personnel holding Level 5 clearance. SCP-4860 is not present on any civilian maps or satellite imagery, nor is it mentioned by any government documents. Limited knowledge of SCP-4860 is possessed by amateur &quot;haunted house&quot; tourist organizations, but this is not believed to pose a significant risk to containment efforts.&quot; This extract doesn't include containment protocols. Containment protocols are imperatives, this is description</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
