					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-11066132#post-4221456</guid>
				<title>Spooky</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-11066132/scp-4860#post-4221456</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2019 03:32:17 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Klaver</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3430235</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Damn this shit is eerie. From what I gathered, the Circus Co. ends up killing kids and adolescents, and uses their body parts to make toy clowns? What the hell. And the fact that no one can enter the &quot;rooms&quot; inside the building? That's even quirkier. This piece is pretty spooky and creates a rather&#8230; well to put it simply, a rather ominous mood over the reader. At least for me anyways.</p> <p>+1!</p> 
				 	]]>
